This is the SyFy version not the feature film version everybody is expecting, as per my comment on TV Teams upload of same today.

But can confirm, this is the SyFy version.

Not a bad SyFy flick imho, though some hated it completely, not feature film budget material but is enjoyable and worth the download if not already seen it.
